#
#  Maintained by Evan "evmar" Martin (evmar/n2).  459 GH stars.  n2
#  ("into") is a NINJA-COMPATIBLE BUILD SYSTEM by Evan Martin — the
#  ORIGINAL AUTHOR of Ninja itself.  n2 reads Ninja's `build.ninja`
