#  modern Rust implementation focused on incremental performance,
#  better debug output, and CMake/Meson compatibility.  Used as a
#  drop-in replacement for `ninja` in CMake/Meson projects where
#  better diagnostic output is desired.  Sister tools: ninja (the
#  original C++ ninja, IN CORPUS + STOCK via _ninja), samurai (C
#  ninja reimplementation), Make (in corpus via _make), Tup (in
